    "description": "《在黑暗中》是一款卡牌构建式类 Rogue 恐怖游戏。收集卡片、技能、物品和灵魂，并用它们来生存。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/c54c5d7b90582b9b04423f0deaf32a81.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br>世界因陨石的撞击而笼罩在黑暗之中，怪物出现了，尸体变成了僵尸。生存的唯一方法就是继续前进。选择三个地方之一。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/3490c483a644add6f38876d2c2a0e883.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>你可以与其他幸存者合作和对抗。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/49fc72e6882af1ea471ba1f6de578edf.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>每当你独自进入安全的地方时，就会出现一个幽灵。另外...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/ff13f596b342468639b25c8aad1086f8.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=240 /></span><br>一大群僵尸是一群强大的敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/051059ffedc08738fd37f6dd540db6c4.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span><br>当你击败怪物领导时，你可以选择结束游戏或继续游戏。请考虑你的空闲时间和成就。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142040/extras/69123cf9aa732c504ed6d2f3af6eb367.avif?t=1710113331\" width=640 height=180 /></span>",
